The paper discusses the use of spintronic sensors in IoT for smart living, which involves monitoring and managing various systems such as power grids, transportation, and healthcare. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.IT (Information Theory). However, given the focus on sensor networks and monitoring systems, cs.ET and cs.SY are the most likely categories, followed by cs.NI, cs.SE, and cs.IT.
